This file contains an ASCII reproduction of the Der Clou! Public License
Contract contained in 'publiclicencecontract.doc'. The reproduction is
provided for the convenience of those which cannot read Microsoft Word '.doc'
format documents.

As far as the author of this port knows, this summarizes the license terms:
* No distribution for profit.
* The licensee must release all source and data additions or changes by
  e-mail to <office@neo.at>, within 14 calendar days after release for
  distribution, with "Open Source" on the subject line.
* The licensee must release publically both a binary, and a developer's
  distribution (source and data).
* The licensee must not misrepresent the product. The licensee must name his
  distribution with "Der Clou!" as a basename. For example.

  Original name:
    Der Clou!

  Possible names:
    Der Clou! - Windows Version V1.0
    Der Clou! - XXX

* Distributions must include the license file 'publiclicensecontract.doc'.


Please remember:
